Hey everyone! I'm a full-stack web and app developer based in Jakarta, Indonesia, formerly Southern California, USA. I primarily work with React.js and React Native. To add some function to my shiny front end I also have experience in Node.js, Express.js, and PostreSQL to complete the stack. I'm a huge fan of lightweight and modular code with functional design in mind, and I have a pension for writing scripts that make my life easier.

I also consider myself a self-taught expert in consumer electronics, a self-proclaimed movie critic, and extremely addicted to YouTube. When I'm not coding, I'm either watching movies/TV Shows, spending time with friends and family, or staying up late to watch tech conferences from different time zones.

I currently work as a full stack software engineer at a fintech startup dedicated to bringing financial and employee wellness to 60% of Indonesia's workforce. My projects include but are not limited to building Open APIs and back end infrastructure, in addition to contributing to the maintenance and improvement our mobile app. Before that, I worked as a data analyst at an AI fintech startup based in California, where I wrote server-side code for collecting and aggegating product data for sentiment analysis that influenced our machine learning model.
